1166: EAB8         ;---------------------------- Reset Disk System - D (13) -------------------;
1167: EAB8         ;  This function requests CP/M to completely reset the disk file system.    ;
1168: EAB8         ; CP/M then resets its internal tables, selects logical disk A as the       ;
1169: EAB8         ; default disk, resets the DMAaddress back to 0080H (the address of the     ;
