1806: EC6C         ; applies to the address of the buffer to and from which data is            ;
1807: EC6C         ; transferred whenever a diskette Read, Write, or directory operation is    ;
1808: EC6C         ; performed. Whenever CP/M first starts up (cold boot) m a warm boot or     ;
1809: EC6C         ; Reset Disk operation occurs, the DMA address is reset to its default      ;
