1840: EC7C         ;---------------------------- Write Protect Disk - 1C (28) -----------------;
1841: EC7C         ;  This function logically sets the currently selected disk to a Read-Only  ;
1842: EC7C         ; state. Any attempts to execute a Write Sequential or Write Random function;
1843: EC7C         ; to the selected disk will be intercepted by the BDOS, and the following   ;
1844: EC7C         ; message will appear on the console:                                       ;
