2022: ECB3         ;------------------------- Write Random - 22 (34) --------------------------;
2023: ECB3         ; This function writes a specific CP/M record (128 bytes) into a random     ;
2024: ECB3         ; file. It is initiated in much the same way as the companion function,     ;
2025: ECB3         ; Read Random (code 33,21H). It assumes that you have already opened the    ;
2026: ECB3         ; file, set the DMAaddress to the address in memory containing the record to;
2027: ECB3         ; be written to disk, and set the random record number in the FCB to the    ;
2028: ECB3         ; specified record being written. This function also computes the extent in ;
2029: ECB3         ; which the specified record number lies and opens the extent (creating it  ;
